Package: lwdid
Title: Lee-Wooldridge Difference-in-Differences Estimation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Xuanyu", "Cai", , "xuanyuCAI@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = "City University of Macau"),
    person("Wenli", "Xu", , "wlxu@cityu.edu.mo", role = "aut",
           comment = "City University of Macau")
    )
Date: 2026-06-20
Description: Implements the Lee and Wooldridge (2025, 2026) simple
    transformation approach for difference-in-differences estimation
    with panel data. Supports both common timing and staggered
    adoption designs with multiple estimators (RA, IPW, IPWRA, PSM).
    Provides robust variance estimation (HC0-HC4, cluster-robust),
    randomization inference, wild cluster bootstrap, and comprehensive
    diagnostic tools for trend analysis, clustering, and selection.
